<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>春天，夏天，秋天，冬天是四个季节。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个季节都不一样，他们有自己特别的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很温暖。植物们很喜欢我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我下雨。”春天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘀嗒，嘀嗒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蝴蝶们很喜欢我，因为我给他们花儿。”春天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红花儿，黄花儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很热。大海很喜欢我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为人们喜欢在海里游泳。”夏天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗哗，哗哗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冰淇淋很喜欢我，因为人们吃冰淇淋。”夏天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>草莓味儿，香草味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很凉爽。叶子很喜欢我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我给他们美丽的颜色。”秋天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红，橙，黄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小松鼠很喜欢我，因为我给他们橡子。”秋天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>捡起来，捡起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很冷。雪很喜欢我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为孩子们在雪地里玩儿。”冬天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪花，雪花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪橇很喜欢我，因为孩子们滑雪橇。”冬天说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>滑呀，滑呀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>春天，夏天，秋天，冬天是四个快乐的季节。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182969</EndMilliseconds>
